ygData.messageBody:
No, that wouldn't be the case. My highest is a lvl 55
and the lowest is 13. I think I just didn't reactivate
my account in time. Oh well. Maybe as the release date
for EQ2 gets closer, they might do this again.


--- Techpriest <techpriest@...> wrote:
> I also did not recieve a key. When I looked into it
> I noticed it said
> player of "mid-level" characters. Since my highest
> is 17 now, I think that
> is why I was left out. Not sure if this matters to
> you, but since the keys
> were sent out starting May 31, you might have missed
> it because of that.
>
> Just a note, all keys not used go bad July 2, so if
> you have one you might
> want to use it or let us know about it pretty soon.
> Would hate to see all
> those keys go bad.
>
